# Protect Environment Files

- NEVER read, open, or display `.env`, `.env.*`, or any environment variable files
- NEVER modify or create `.env` files
- If a user asks about env variables, help with the variable name or structure without accessing the actual file
- When debugging env-related issues, ask the user to verify values themselves
